===Pronunciation===
אביעזר / 'ăbîy‛ezer / ab-ee-ay'-zer

===Etymology===
From [[אב]] {{HH|1}} and [[עזר]] {{HH|5829}}; [[father]] of [[help]] (that is, helpful); 

===Proper noun===
'''אביעזר'''

# Abiezer, the name of two Israelites: - [[Abiezer]].

